				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<h1 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">The Banality of Surveillance</h1>		</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fdbbf71 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="fdbbf71" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>Two new books examine the ordinary roots of our extraordinary regime of high-tech monitoring.</p>
					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2da098b greenAuthor elementor-widget elementor-widget-toolset-view" data-id="2da098b" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="toolset-view.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			



	
	
	
		<a class="authorlink" href="https://bostonreview.net/authors/sophia-goodfriend/" data-wpel-link="internal">
  <span class="author">
    Sophia Goodfriend
  </span>
</a>

	
	
	

