      <h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">
        <a href="https://bostonreview.net/articles/my-grandfather-was-a-virus/" data-wpel-link="internal">My grandfather was a virus</a>
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p style="font-weight: 400;">I was also spat across an ocean</p>
<p style="font-weight: 400;">and clung to the edge of an unwilling continent.</p>

    </div>
    <div class="relatedAuthor">
      



	
	
	
		<span class="author">
  Caio Kaufman
