  <div class="content-wrap">
    <div class="elementor-widget-heading">
      <h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">
        <a href="https://bostonreview.net/articles/reconsidering-the-good-life/" data-wpel-link="internal">Reconsidering the Good Life</a>
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>Feminist philosophers Kate Soper and Lynne Segal discuss the unsustainable obsession with economic growth and consider what it might look like if we all worked less.</p>

    </div>
    <div class="relatedAuthor">
      



	
	
	
		<span class="author">
  Lynne Segal
</span>

	
		<span class="author">
  Kate Soper
</span>

	
		<span class="author">
  Anthony Morgan
</span>

	
	
	


